Masu ruwa da tsaki na hukumar sun ce mutane da dama sun makale a karkashin tarwatsewar gine-ginen da suka rushe sakamakon girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5, inda raƙuman ruwa suka kai kafa 20 a lokacin girgizar.
