John Goldsmith, shugaban Ƙungiyar Cromwell, ya ce: "Taron da ake yi yanzu game da cire mutum-mutumi ya sa ya zama dole a yi amfani da shi wajen kawar da mutum-mutumi na Oliver Cromwell da ke fadar Westminster.
Ba a taɓa yin bautar gumaka a lokacin yakin basasa na Ingila ba bisa umurnin Cromwell, kuma Cromwell bai yi ba.
Cromwell ba daidai ba ne, wanda ya zama hadaya ga abubuwan da magajinsa Thomas Cromwell ya yi a karni na karshe.
Cromwell mutum-mutumi mai ban mamaki wanda Sir William Hammock Thonycroft ya yi shine hujja ga ra'ayi na karni na 19 game da Cromwell kuma wani ɓangare na tarihin wani shugaban da mutane da yawa har yanzu suna ganin yana da daraja a yi bikin.
Mr. Goldsmith ya gaya wa The Sunday Telegraph: "A ƙarshen karni na sha tara, mutane da yawa, wataƙila mutane da yawa, sun ɗauki Cromwell a matsayin wanda ya kāre majalisar daga matsin lamba daga waje fiye da yadda yake a yau, yayin da yake mulkin mallaka.
