Za mu iya tsammanin babban misali na canjin yanayin zafi a tsakiyar Amurka a ranar Lahadi.
Akwai bambancin zafin jiki na kusan digiri 20 tsakanin Kansas City, Missouri, Omaha, da Nebraska, da tsakanin St. Louis, Des Moines, da Iowa.
A cikin 'yan kwanaki masu zuwa, za a fara sake buɗewa da kuma fadada yanayin bazara.
Ana sa ran Oktoba za ta fara da zafi a yawancin tsakiyar Amurka da gabashin Amurka, tare da zafin jiki na digiri 80 daga kudancin filayen zuwa yankunan arewa maso gabas.
A ranar Talata zafin jiki a birnin New York zai kai digiri 80, wanda zai iya zama kusan digiri 10 sama da matsakaita.
Hasashenmu na dogon lokaci ya nuna cewa zafin jiki zai iya zama sama da matsakaici a yammacin Amurka har zuwa farkon rabin watan Oktoba.
Mutane sama da miliyan 20 ne suka kalli shari'ar Brett Kavanaugh.
Mutane fiye da miliyan 20 sun ga shaidar da aka bayar a gaban kotun, ta Brett Kavanaugh, wanda aka zaba a Kotun Koli, da kuma Christine Blasey Ford, wata mata da ta zargi cibiyoyin talabijin shida cewa Brett Kavanaugh ya yi lalata da ita a 1980.
A halin yanzu, yayin da masu watsa shirye-shirye suka katse shirye-shiryen yau da kullun don juyawa na ƙarshe a ranar Juma'a, jam'iyyun siyasa sun ci gaba da nisanta kansu da batun; juyawa ta kasance yarjejeniya da Sanata Jeff Flake na Arizona ya yi cewa FBI za ta gudanar da binciken mako guda game da zargin.
Ford ya shaida wa kwamitin shari'a cewa yana da tabbacin cewa Kavanaugh ya shiga cikin wani biki na makarantar sakandare kuma ya yi ƙoƙarin cire tufafinsa.
Kavanaugh ya ce yana da tabbaci cewa hakan bai faru ba.
A ranar Juma'a, Nielsen ta ruwaito cewa mutane sama da miliyan 20.4 ne suka kalli bidiyon.
Kamfanin ya ƙidaya matsakaicin yawan kallo a CBS, ABC, NBC, CNN, Fox News Channel, MSNBC.
Bayanan kallo daga cibiyoyin sadarwa na Met da suka watsa wannan labarin, ciki har da PBS, C-SPAN da Fox Business Network, har yanzu ba su samu ba.
Bugu da ƙari, Nielsen yana da matsala na fasaha don ɗaukar yawan mutanen da ke zaune a ofisoshi suna kallon shirye-shiryen TV.
Idan muka yi la'akari da shi, yana da masu sauraro masu yawa kamar kallon wasan kwallon kafa ko kuma bikin bayar da lambar yabo ta Academy.
Fox News Channel ta nuna goyon baya sosai ga nadin Kavanaugh, wanda ya haifar da matsakaicin masu kallo miliyan 5.69 a duk hanyoyin sadarwa a lokacin shari'ar ranar, in ji Nielsen.
ABC ne na biyu tare da masu kallo miliyan 3.26
Nielsen ya ce CBS ta samu masu kallo miliyan 3.1 yayin da NBC ta samu miliyan 2.94, MS NBC ta samu miliyan 2.89 da CNN ta samu miliyan 2.52.
Bayan shari'ar, sha'awar jama'a game da batun ta ci gaba da ƙaruwa.
Flake ne babban jarumin wasan kwaikwayo na ranar Juma'a.
Ofishin wannan dan Republican mai tsaka-tsakin yanayi ya fitar da wata sanarwa da ta ce zai kada kuri'a a madadin Kavanaugh, kuma kyamarorin CNN da CBS sun kama shi da sautin zanga-zangar da ake yi a kan shi yayin da yake kokarin hawa lif don fuskantar shari'ar kwamitin shari'a a safiyar ranar Juma'a.
CNN ta nuna shi yana kallon ƙasa na mintuna da yawa yayin da mutane ke magana da shi cikin fushi.
"Ina tsaye a gabanka", wata mata ta ce.
"Kana ganin yana gaya wa kasar gaskiya ne?
"Kana da iko lokacin da mata da yawa ba su da ƙarfi", wani ya ce masa.
Flake ya ce ofishinsa ya fitar da wata sanarwa kuma yana da karin bayani a taron kwamitin, kafin a rufe kofar lif din.
Daga bisani, yayin da kwamitin ke jefa kuri'ar yanke shawara kan ko za a ci gaba da neman takarar Kavanaugh zuwa majalisar dattijai don jefa kuri'a, dukkan cibiyoyin sadarwar igiyar ruwa da na watsa shirye-shirye sun watsa shi kai tsaye.
Amma Flake ya ce zai yi hakan ne kawai a kan cewa FBI za ta gabatar da zarge-zarge game da wanda aka zaba a mako mai zuwa, wanda 'yan Democrat suka bukaci.
Flake ya sami tabbacin hakan ne ta hanyar tattaunawa da abokinsa, Sanata Chris Coons na Democratic.
Bayan tattaunawa da Kruns da wasu sanatoci, Flake ya yanke shawarar.
Flake ya yanke shawarar da ta dace, domin a bayyane yake cewa jam'iyyar Republican ba ta da kuri'un da za ta amince da Kavanaugh ba tare da bincike ba.
Shugaba Trump ya bukaci FBI ta gudanar da bincike kan zargin da ake yi wa Kavanaugh.
Firaministan Burtaniya ya ce masu sukar Brexit suna 'yin siyasa'
A wata hira da jaridar Sunday Times, Firayim Minista Theresa May ta zargi masu sukar shirin ta na ficewa daga Tarayyar Turai da 'yin siyasa' da kuma nuna rashin kula da bukatun kasa a kan makomar Birtaniya.
Firayim Minista Theresa May za ta halarci taron jam'iyyar Conservative Party a Birmingham, Burtaniya, ranar 29 ga Satumba, 2019.
A shafin farko na hirar da Theresa May ta yi, an kuma wallafa hirar da tsohon sakataren harkokin wajen Theresa, Boris Johnson, wanda ya kara tsananta kai hare-haren da ake yi wa shirin 'Checkers Plan for Brexit' na Theresa, inda ya kira shawarar da Birtaniya da EU suka dauka na tara haraji a kan juna 'abin kunya ne gaba daya'.
Yan sanda sun kama wani mutum da ake zargi da laifin kashe dan wasan LSU, Dayton Simpson.
'Yan sanda sun kama wani mutum da ake zargi da harbin da ya kashe dan wasan kwando na LSU mai shekaru 20 Wade De Sims.
An kama wani mutum mai suna Dayton Simpson, mai shekaru 20, da laifin kisan kai na biyu kuma an tsare shi a gidan yari, in ji 'yan sanda a Baton Rouge.
Hukumomi sun fitar da bidiyon gwagwarmayar da aka yi tsakanin Simpson da Simpson, kuma 'yan sanda sun ce Sims ya rasa tabarau a lokacin da aka buge shi.
'Yan sanda sun gano tabarau a wurin kisan, kuma sun gano cewa sun hada da kwayar halittar Simpson, kamar yadda WAFB, 'yar'uwar CBS ta ruwaito.
A lokacin da aka yi wa Simpson tambayoyi, 'yan sanda sun ce ya yarda cewa shi ne ya harbe Wade har lahira.
Lauyan ya ce ya kamata a ba shi belin dala 350,000.
Ofishin mai binciken da ke yankin East Baton Rouge ya bayar da rahoton farko a ranar Juma'a cewa, wanda ya mutu, ya ji rauni ne daga harsashi a kansa zuwa wuyansa.
Ma'aikatar ta gode wa 'yan sanda na jihar Louisiana Fugitive Task Force, 'yan sanda na jihar Crime Lab, 'yan sanda na Jami'ar Southern da kuma' yan ƙasa don taimaka musu wajen gudanar da bincike don kama shi.
Daraktan LSU Lattice Joe Aleva ya gode wa jami'an tsaro a yankin saboda "aikin da suka yi na yin aiki da hankali da kuma kokarin da suka yi na tabbatar da adalci".
