Bayan shekara guda da Madrid ta ayyana zaben na ranar 1 ga watan Oktoba a matsayin haramtacce, amma Catalans da ke goyon bayan raba yankin sun yi bikin zaben, rikici ya ci gaba da kasancewa a yankunan da ke da 'yanci.
Ko da yake yawancin masu jefa kuri'a sun goyi bayan zama 'yanci, yawancin masu adawa da raba sun tsaya a baya, saboda haka yawan masu jefa kuri'a ya kasance kadan.
A cewar hukumomin Catalonia, kusan mutane dubu daya ne suka kamu da cutar a shekarar da ta gabata, wadanda suka jikkata a wasu fadace-fadace da aka yi a lokacin da 'yan sanda ke kokarin kawo karshen zaben a wuraren zabe a fadin yankin.
