Narcis Termez, mai shekara 68, wanda ya halarci zanga-zangar 'yan adawa da matarsa, ya ce ba shi da bege game da makomar Catalonia na samun 'yanci.
"A shekarar da ta gabata mun yi rayuwa mafi kyau a rayuwarmu.
Na ga iyayena masu addini suna kuka saboda farin cikin samun damar zabe, amma yanzu muna cikin damuwa", in ji shi.
Duk da samun gagarumar nasara a zaben kananan hukumomi da aka yi a watan Disamba da ya gabata, jam'iyyun da ke goyon bayan 'yancin kai na Catalonia na fama da samun ci gaba a wannan shekara, saboda wasu daga cikin fitattun shugabannin sun tsere ko kuma wasu shugabannin suna tsare a kurkuku suna jiran hukunci saboda rawar da suka taka wajen shirya kuri'ar raba gardama da kuma sanar da 'yancin kai.
