Girgizar kasa da tsunami sun kashe daruruwan mutane a Indonesia, kuma adadin wadanda suka mutu yana ƙaruwa
A kalla mutane 384 sun mutu a ranar Asabar, a cewar hukumomi, yayin da manyan raƙuman ruwa da tsunami suka mamaye bakin teku a tsibirin Sulawesi na Indonesia.
A ranar Juma'a da yamma, sa'ad da daruruwan mutane suka taru don bikin a garin Palu, raƙuman ruwa masu tsayi mita shida (18 feet) suka mamaye bakin teku, suka lalata duk abin da ke gaban su, kuma daruruwan sun mutu a cikin ambaliyar.
Tsunami ya biyo bayan girgizar kasa mai karfin awo 7.5.
"A jiya lokacin da barazanar tsunami ta tashi, mutane suna bakin rairayin bakin teku, wadanda suka mutu mutane ne da ba su gudu da sauri ba saboda gargadin", in ji mai magana da yawun hukumar kula da bala'in Indonesia, BNPB, Sutopo Parwo Nugroho a Jakarta.
"Ba wai kawai tsunami ya zo ba, ya mamaye motoci, bishiyoyi, gidaje, ya faɗi a kan komai a ƙasa", in ji Nugroho, yana mai ƙara cewa tsunami ya yi tafiya a cikin teku mai sauri da sauri a cikin kilomita 800 a kowace awa (miso 497 a kowace awa) kafin ya faɗi bakin teku.
Ya ce wasu mutane sun hau kan bishiyoyi don tsira daga tsunami kuma sun tsira.
An kwashe mutane kusan 16,700 zuwa cibiyoyi 24 a Palau.
Hotunan sama da hukumar kula da bala'i ta fitar sun nuna gine-gine da shaguna da dama da suka lalace, ginshiƙan da suka rushe da kuma masallacin musulmi da ke cikin ruwa.
A ranar Asabar, manyan raƙuman ruwa da suka biyo bayan ƙarshen tsunami sun ci gaba da buga rairayin bakin teku.
An ji girgizar ƙasa a wani yanki da mutane 2.4 ke zaune.
Hukumar Indonesia ta BPPT ta ce girgizar kasar da ta auku a ranar Juma'a ta fi karfin bam din nukiliya da aka harba a Hiroshima sau 200 a lokacin yakin duniya na biyu.
Hukumar ta ce, yanayin garin da ke kan gabar teku mai tsayi da kunkuntar teku, na iya kara karfin tsunami.
NuGroho ya ce lalacewar ta kasance "mai yawa" kuma dubban gidaje, asibitoci, cibiyoyin kasuwanci da otal-otal sun lalace.
Ya ce an gano wasu gawarwakin wadanda suka mutu a karkashin gine-ginen da suka rushe, an samu raunuka 540 da kuma rasa mutane 29.
