A halin yanzu, ba za a iya musanta cewa harsuna za su ci gaba da kasancewa muhimmiyar mahimmanci ga makomar ƙasar ba a cikin yanayin kasuwancin duniya, don haka ya kamata a nuna hakan a cikin ilimi.
Hakika, ya kamata a ɗauki harsuna na zamani a matsayin "ƙwarewar sadarwa ta duniya".
Makarantun kyauta za su ci gaba da samar da wannan zaɓi, bambancin da kyau ga yara a Scotland.
"Idan ba ku yi ba, to, ku yi ba".
John Edward ne darektan na Scottish Council na Independent Schools.
LeBron zai buga wa Lakers wasa a San Diego ranar Lahadi.
Wannan shi ne lokacin da magoya bayan kungiyar Lakers suka fara jiran LeBron James ya fara buga wasan.
Kocin Lakers Luke Walton ya sanar da cewa James zai buga wasan farko na kakar wasa a ranar Lahadi da Denver Nuggets a San Diego.
Amma ba a san tsawon lokacin da James zai yi a wasan ba.
"Lokaci zai kasance da minti daya da minti 48", in ji Walton a shafin yanar gizon Lakers.
Mai ba da rahoto na Lakers Mike Trudell ya wallafa cewa James zai buga wasa na iyakantaccen lokaci.
Bayan na farko na wannan makon, James ya tambayi game da Lakers ta shida-wasa pre-kakar jadawalin.
"Ba na bukatar wasannin kakar wasa a wannan lokacin a aikina don shirya", in ji shi.
Lokacin taron Trump na West Virginia, tashar YouTube
A wannan karon a birnin Wheeling na jihar West Virginia, Shugaba Donald Trump zai fara gangamin yakin neman zabensa.
Wannan shi ne na farko daga cikin gangamin Trump guda biyar da aka shirya a mako mai zuwa a wurare masu yawan mabiya, ciki har da Tennessee da Mississippi.
Baya ga tabbatar da kuri'ar da za a kada wa dan takararsa a kotun koli, Trump na da niyyar kara yawan goyon baya a gaban zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba, saboda akwai fargabar cewa jam'iyyar Republican za ta rasa iko a majalisar dokoki a lokacin zaben da za a yi a watan Nuwamba.
A wane lokaci ne za ku iya kallon taron Trump a yammacin Virginia a kan layi?
An shirya taron Trump a Wheeling, West Virginia a ranar Asabar, 29 ga Satumba, 2018 da karfe 7 na yamma (Lokacin Gabas).
Za ku iya kallon taron Trump na West Virginia a YouTube a nan.
Trump na iya yin tsokaci game da shari'ar wannan makon game da wanda aka zaba a Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ake zargi da laifin lalata da aka yi wa Kavanaugh, wanda aka dage zaben tabbatar da majalisar dattijai har zuwa mako guda saboda binciken FBI.
Amma babban burin wannan taron shine samar da wani karamin ci gaba ga jam'iyyar Republican da ke fuskantar zaben watan Nuwamba.
Saboda haka, masu goyon bayan yakin neman zaben Shugaba Trump sun ce, taron gangamin da za a yi a mako mai zuwa, na nufin "karfafa masu sa kai da magoya baya, yayin da jam'iyyar ke kokarin rikewa da karawa jam'iyyar Republican rinjaye a majalisar wakilai", in ji Reuters.
"Sarrafawa majalisa tana da matukar muhimmanci ga ajandar shugaban kasa, don haka yayin da muke zafafa yakin neman zabe, zai ziyarci jihohi da dama", in ji wani kakakin yakin neman zaben Trump ga Reuters, amma ya ki bayyana sunansa.
A cewar West Virginia Metro News, gangamin da za a yi a gidan wasan Wesleyan Co. Arena a Wheeling, Ohio, zai jawo hankalin magoya baya daga Ohio da Pennsylvania kuma ya sami hankalin kafofin watsa labarai na Pittsburgh.
A watan da ya gabata, Trump ya ziyarci jihar West Virginia, wanda zai zama ziyararsa ta biyu tare da taron ranar Asabar, inda ya lashe zaben 2016 da kashi 40 cikin dari na kuri'un da aka kada.
Trump yana kokarin taimaka wa dan takarar majalisar dattijai na West Virginia, Patrick Morrissey, wanda ya samu koma baya a kuri'un masu kada kuri'a.
"Ba alama ce mai kyau ba ga shugaban kasa ya samu nasara a zaben shugaban kasa, "in ji Simon Heider, masanin kimiyyar siyasa a Jami'ar West Virginia, ga Reuters.
Ryder Cup 2018: Team USA ta nuna halin gwagwarmaya don ci gaba da tsammanin yayin da ta shiga wasan kwaikwayo na ranar Lahadi
Bayan zaman uku na rashin daidaito, watakila wannan karon gasar Ryder ta samu nasarar kammala gasar.
Ko da yake yanayin wasan yana da matukar damuwa, amma yana da wani abu da 'yan wasan suka gaskata, musamman a wasanni kamar wannan.
To, ina ne wannan fa'ida take yanzu?
"Sun kasance maki shida a gaba, yanzu hudu, don haka ina tsammanin yana da karamin ci gaba a gare mu", in ji Jordan Speith yayin da yake tafiya bayan wasan.
A wasan da aka buga sau 12, Turai tana da ci gaba da maki hudu.
Duk da haka, kamar yadda Speeth ya ce, Amurkawa suna jin cewa iska tana da kyau a gare su kuma suna da yawa don yin ƙarfin hali. Ba su da wata damuwa game da wasan da Speeth da Justin Thomas suka yi.
A cikin fim din "From Tea to Green", Speeth, wanda ya kasance mai kisa, ya zama misali ga sauran.
Bayan wasanni biyu da aka buga, Speeth da Thomas sun kasance a baya da maki biyu, kuma bikin ya kara da ƙarfi lokacin da Speeth ya yi wani muhimmin abu don kawo wasan zuwa hudu.
An yi wa karen nasa irin wannan ihu da ya lashe gasar a ranar 15 ga watan Nuwamba, kuma wannan ihu ya kasance a kan bene yana gaya wa mutane cewa ya yi imanin cewa ba a fitar da tawagar Amurka daga wasan ba.
"Abin da ya kamata ka yi shi ne ka san yadda kake wasa da kuma damuwarka", in ji Speeth.
Wannan shi ne abin da kowane dan wasa ke da shi yanzu.
Ramin 18 don nuna inganci.
Francesco Molinari da Tommy Fleetwood ne kawai 'yan wasa da suka fi Speed da Thomas maki a cikin kwanaki biyu da suka gabata, tarihin Ryder Cup.
Waɗannan tagwaye ba za su yi kuskure ba tare da raba Turai da kuma bauta wa wanda ya lashe hudu daga cikin hudu.
Sai dai kuma sun yi watsi da wasan da suka buga a safiyar Asabar da yamma, sannan suka yi wasan karshe a ranar Jumma'a da safe.
Wannan wasan da yadda suke da karfi da kuma yadda suke da karfi a cikin taron jama'a suna nuna cewa su ne 'yan wasan da za su ci nasara a ranar Lahadi. Babu wani dan wasa da ya fi Fleetwood ko Molinari shahara wajen tabbatar da nasarar Turai a lokacin da rana ta faɗi a kan Le Golf National.
Zai fi kyau su yi wasa a wurare dabam-dabam a lokaci guda.
Duk da haka, magana game da darajar Turai ya kasance ba a kan lokaci ba.
Sergio Garcia, jarumin wasan kwaikwayo na safe, wanda ya yi wasa tare da Alex Noran, ya yi nasara da Bubba Watson da Web Simpson.
A cikin ramuka tara na farko, wani bogey da biyu biyu sun tura Spaniard da Swede cikin rami wanda ba za a iya hawa ba.
Amma a ranar Lahadi, babu wanda zai iya fitar da ku daga rami.
Abinda ya fi ban sha'awa a kusa da ForBalls da ForSums shine yadda suke hulɗa da juna, da shawarar da suke ba da juna, da shawarar da ba su ba, da kuma yadda kowane irin dabara zai iya canzawa a cikin minti daya.
Turai, wacce ta yi nasara a matsayin ta, ta ci gaba da samun nasara a ranar karshe, amma wannan zaman na farko ya nuna cewa Team Amurka, wanda wasu, musamman ma kasarsu, sun yi shakkar cewa tana da ƙarfin hali.
Turai ta ci gaba da ci 10-6 a wasan Ryder Cup
Turai ta fito daga wasannin kwallon kafa da na wasa na ranar Asabar da ta yi nasara da Amurka da ci 10 da 6.
Tommy Fleetwood da Francesco Molinari sun jagoranci nasarar da suka samu a kan Tiger Woods wanda ke fama da fama da shan wahala, wanda ya jagoranci nasarar da suka samu a kan Le Golf National zuwa maki hudu.
A gasar da suka yi a Haseltine shekaru biyu da suka gabata, kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Turai ta Thomas Jordan ta yi nasarar doke kungiyar kwallon kafa ta Amurka da ta yi nasara a wasan da suka yi a Haseltine.
Duk da cewa Amurka ta fi karfin iko a gasar, ta lashe wasanni biyu, amma ba ta iya ragewa ba.
Jim Furyk yana bukatar maki takwas daga cikin 12 da zai buga a wasan da zai yi a ranar Lahadi idan yana son ya ci gasar.
Fleetwood shine farkon sabon shiga Turai wanda ya ci kwallaye hudu a jere. A halin yanzu, shi da Molinari, wanda aka kira "Mollywood" bayan karshen mako mai ban sha'awa, sune kawai biyu biyu a tarihin Ryder Cup don samun maki hudu daga wasanninsu na farko.
Bayan sun doke Woods da Patrick Reed a wasan gaba, sai suka hada kai don doke Woods da aka rasa amincewa da shi da kuma sabon dan Amurka, Bryson DeCambu, a kan 5 & 4 mai karfi.
Woods ya yi wasa biyu a ranar Asabar, ya nuna fashewar nasara, amma yanzu ya rasa wasanni 19 daga cikin 29 a wasan gaba da na hudu, bakwai a jere.
Bayan ya huta da safe don wasan motsa jiki, Justin Rose ya koma tare da Henrik Stenson a wasan motsa jiki don doke Dustin Johnson da Brooks Koepke a 2 & 1 a matsayin na farko da na uku a duniya.
Duk da haka, a wannan rana mai kyau, mai iska a kudu maso yammacin Paris, Turai ba ta iya samun komai ba.
Jordan Speight da Justin Thomas, wadanda suka lashe manyan wasanni uku, sun kafa maki biyu a ranar Asabar.
A cikin wasan kwaikwayo, sun sami nasara a kan John Rahm da Ian Poulter na Spain, wanda ya ci nasara a kan 2 & 1 , sannan kuma Poulter da Rory McElroy a cikin wasan kwaikwayo, sun rasa ramuka biyu na farko, sun dawo don doke 4 & 3.
Duk da cewa Fury's na bukatar a tashi wasa daya domin rike kofin, sau biyu ne kawai a tarihin gasar Ryder Cup da wata kungiya ta dawo daga rashin ci hudu a wasan da ta buga a wasan aure.
Ko da yake sun ci gaba da zama na biyu a rana ta biyu, amma suna ganin za su shawo kan wannan hari a ranar Lahadi.
Koriya ta Arewa ta ce "babu wata hanyar da za ta samu makaman yaki a bangare daya" saboda rashin amincewa
Ministan harkokin wajen Koriya ta Arewa ya shaida wa Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a ranar Asabar cewa ci gaba da takunkumi yana kara rashin amincewa da Amurka kuma a irin wannan yanayi babu wata hanyar da kasar za ta yi watsi da makaman nukiliya ba tare da wani bangare ba.
A shekarar da ta gabata, Koriya ta Arewa ta dauki "matakai masu muhimmanci don mutunta mutuncinta", ta ce a taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya na shekara-shekara, ta fara da dakatar da gwajin makaman nukiliya da na makaman nukiliya, rushe wurin gwajin makaman nukiliya, da kuma yin alkawarin ba za a kara fadada makaman nukiliya da fasahar nukiliya ba.
Ya ce, "Duk da haka, ba mu ga irin wannan martani daga Amurka ba".
"Ba za mu iya amincewa da tsaron kasa ba idan ba mu da amincewa da Amurka, kuma a irin wannan yanayi ba mu da wata hanyar da za mu iya kawar da kanmu da farko".
Ko da yake Ri ya sake maimaita sanannun korafe-korafen Koriya ta Arewa game da juriya da Washington ke nunawa game da tsarin tsarin nukiliya na "mataki-mataki", amma ba a yi watsi da cewa ba a yi amfani da makaman nukiliya ba kamar yadda Pyongyang ta yi a baya.
Ri ya ambaci cewa, a taron da suka yi a Singapore a ranar 12 ga watan Yuni, Kim Jong Un da Donald Trump sun fitar da wata sanarwa ta hadin gwiwa, wadda ta nuna cewa Kim ya yi alkawarin yin aiki don kawar da makaman nukiliya a yankin Koriya ta Kudu, kuma Trump ya yi alkawarin tabbatar da tsaron Koriya ta Arewa. Wannan taron ne karo na farko da wani shugaban Amurka da shugaban Koriya ta Arewa suka hadu.
Ko da yake Koriya ta Arewa na kokarin kawo karshen yakin Koriya na 1950-53, Amurka ta ce Pyongyang ta fara watsi da makaman nukiliya.
Washington ta kuma yi tir da kiran da ake yi na sassauta takunkumin da ake yi wa Koriya ta Arewa.
"Amurka ta tilasta 'Nuclear Disarmament First' da kuma kara matsin lamba ta hanyar takunkumi don cimma burinsu ta hanyar karfi, har ma da adawa da 'sanarwar cewa an kawo karshen yakin,'" in ji Ri.
"Tunanin cewa za mu durƙusa a ƙarƙashin takunkumi mafarki ne na mutane da ba su san mu ba.
Matsalar ita ce, rashin amincewarmu yana ƙaruwa saboda takunkumi da ake ci gaba da yi".
Ri bai ambaci shirin taron karawa juna sani na biyu tsakanin Kim da Trump ba, wanda shugaban Amurka ya yi magana a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a makon da ya gabata.
Maimakon haka, ya ambaci ganawar da Kim da shugaban Koriya ta Kudu Moon Jae-in suka yi sau uku a cikin watanni biyar da suka gabata, ministan ya kara da cewa, "Koriya ta Kudu ce ta dauki wannan matakin na kawar da makaman nukiliya, ba Amurka ba, saboda haka, ba za a taba samun irin wannan matsala ba a yankin Koriya ta Kudu.
Duk da haka, sautin jawabin Ri a yanzu ya bambanta sosai da sautin da ya yi a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a bara. Ri ya ce a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa kiran Kim "Mr. Shaidan Shugaba" wani yunƙurin kashe kansa ne kuma saboda haka, rokoki na Koriya ta Arewa da ke nufin Amurka suna da muhimmanci.
Trump, wanda ya yi barazanar lalata Koriya ta Arewa gaba daya a bara, ya yi wa Kim yabo a Majalisar Dinkin Duniya a wannan shekara saboda ƙarfin hali da ya nuna wajen daukar matakan kwantar da hankali, amma ya ce akwai sauran matakai da yawa da za a dauka kuma dole ne a ci gaba da takunkumi har sai Koriya ta Arewa ta kammala aikin ta na nukiliya.
A ranar Laraba, Trump ya ce babu wani lokaci da aka tsara, ya kara da cewa, "Ko dai ya dauki shekaru biyu ko uku ko watanni biyar, ba matsala".
China da Rasha sun bukaci kwamitin sulhu na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ya ba Pyongyang lada saboda matakan da ta dauka.
Duk da haka, a ranar Alhamis, Sakataren Harkokin Wajen Amurka Mike Pompeo ya gaya wa Kwamitin Tsaro na Majalisar Dinkin Duniya cewa: "Ya kamata a ci gaba da aiwatar da takunkumin da Kwamitin Tsaro ya tsara har sai an cimma cikakken, karshe da tabbataccen makaman nukiliya".
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta dage takunkumin da ta kakaba wa Koriya ta Arewa tun 2006 domin dakatar da kudaden da take baiwa Pyongyang don ci gaba da ayyukan nukiliyarta da makaman ta.
Pompeo ya gana da shi a kan hanyar Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, kuma daga baya ya ce zai sake ziyartar Pyongyang a watan gobe don shirya taron na biyu.
Pompeo ya ziyarci Koriya ta Arewa sau uku a wannan shekarar, amma ziyarar da ya yi ta ƙarshe ba ta yi nasara ba.
Ko da yake ya bar Pyongyang yana cewa akwai ci gaba, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi tir da cewa ya gabatar da "buƙatun da suka yi kama da na 'yan daba" a cikin kwari bayan ya tafi.
A wani taron da suka yi da Moon a watan jiya, Koriya ta Arewa ta yi alkawarin cewa za ta rushe wani wurin da take amfani da makamai masu linzami da kuma makaman nukiliya idan Amurka ta dauki irin wannan matakin.
Ya ce Kim ya gaya masa cewa ana bukatar irin wannan matakin ne don tabbatar da tsaro da aka tabbatar a Singapore da kuma komawa ga daidaita dangantakar da ke tsakanin kasar da Washington.
Daliban Harvard suna koyon yadda za su samu isasshen barci.
A wannan shekara, an gabatar da sabon darasi ga dukkan daliban Jami'ar Harvard don samun karin barci, a matsayin wani mataki na yaki da al'adun 'macho' da ke ci gaba da bunkasa, wanda ke haifar da yawan shan maganin kafeyin da kuma yin barci a duk dare.
Wani masanin kimiyya ya gano cewa ɗalibai a babbar jami'a a duniya galibi ba su da tabbas game da yadda za su kula da kansu.
Charles Sizler, Farfesa a Magungunan Barci a Makarantar Likita ta Harvard da kuma kwararre a asibitin Brigham da Women's, ya tsara wannan kwas ɗin, wanda ya yi imanin cewa shine farkon irin sa a Amurka.
Ya samu wahayi zuwa ga wannan kwas bayan ya ba da jawabi game da yadda rashin barci ke shafar ilmantarwa.
"A ƙarshen jawabin, wata yarinya ta zo wurina kuma ta ce, 'Ni 'yar shekara ta ƙarshe ce, me ya sa za ki gaya mini haka yanzu?'
Ta ce babu wanda ya gaya mata game da muhimmancin barci - wannan ya ba ni mamaki, 'in ji shi ga The Telegraph.
An gabatar da wannan kwas din a karon farko a wannan shekarar, yana ba wa ɗalibai mahimman bayanai game da yadda al'adun bacci mai kyau ke taimakawa a cikin ilimi, yana taimakawa aikin motsa jiki da haɓaka lafiyar su gaba ɗaya.
Paul Barrera, Farfesa a fannin ilimin halin ƙwaƙwalwa a Harvard Medical School kuma darektan zartarwa na Jami'ar Kula da Lafiya, ya ce jami'ar ta yanke shawarar gabatar da karatun ne bayan da aka gano cewa ɗalibai suna fama da rashin bacci sosai a lokacin mako.
Wannan darasi na awa daya ya kunshi jerin ayyuka masu ma'amala.
A wani sashe akwai hoto na ɗakin gida inda ɗalibai ke danna kofi, labule, masu koyarwa, littattafai, suna iya jin game da tasirin maganin kafeyin da haske, yadda rashin bacci ke shafar aikin lattic, da mahimmancin tsarin bacci.
Wani sashe kuma ya bayyana wa ɗalibai yadda rashin barci na dogon lokaci ke ƙara haɗarin ciwon zuciya, bugun zuciya, baƙin ciki, da kuma ciwon daji.
Bayan haka, taswirar harabar makarantar tare da gumakan ma'amala, yana ƙarfafa ɗalibai suyi tunani game da ayyukansu na yau da kullun.
"Mun san cewa hakan ba zai canza halayyar daliban nan da nan ba.
Amma mun yi imanin cewa suna da 'yancin sanin, kamar yadda kuke da hakkin sanin sakamakon shan taba a kan lafiyar ku,' in ji Farfesa Sisler.
Ya ce har yanzu akwai al'adun da ke alfahari da cewa 'na koyi ba tare da barci ba' kuma cewa fasahar zamani da karuwar matsin lamba a kan dalibai na nufin rashin bacci matsala ce mai girma.
Tabbatar da samun isasshen bacci mai inganci ya kamata ya zama 'makamin sirri' na ɗalibi don magance damuwa, gajiya da damuwa, in ji shi - lokacin da ba mu barci don kauce wa kiba, muna tura kwakwalwarmu cikin yanayin yunwa, wanda ke haifar da yunwa mai ɗorewa.
Raymond Shaw, wani ɗan shekara 19 daga California wanda ke nazarin ilimin sunadarai da ilimin halitta, ya taimaka wa Farfesa Sisler wajen tsara tsarin, kuma Raymond ya halarci wannan aji a shekararsa ta farko a Harvard a bara.
Ya ce wannan kwas din ya bude idanunsa kuma ya karfafa wa dukkanin harabar makarantar gwiwa don gudanar da wannan kwas din.
Mataki na gaba, yana fatan cewa za a nemi dukkan daliban da suka kammala karatun digiri su kammala irin wannan shirin karatun kafin su shiga wata cibiya mai zaman kanta.
Farfesa Sisler ya ba da shawarar cewa ɗalibai suyi la'akari da saita ƙararrawa don sanar da lokacin da za su yi barci da lokacin da za su farka kuma su san illolin 'hasken shuɗi' da allon lantarki da hasken LED ke fitarwa; wannan hasken shuɗi zai iya lalata tsarin sirkadian ku daga al'ada, sannan kuma zai haifar da matsaloli don yin barci.
Livingston 1 - 0 Rangers: Menga ya ci gaba da cin nasarar Gerrard
A lokacin da Dolly Menga ta bar Steven Gerrard ya yi nasara a wasan da ya yi a Livingston, Rangers sun sake jin dadin kasancewa daga cikin gidajensu.
Ibrooks ta nemi ta samu nasarar cin nasara a gasar tun bayan nasarar da ta samu a St Johnstone da ta doke ta da 4-1 a watan Fabrairu. Amma kungiyar ta Gary Holt ta sha kashi biyu a wasa 18 da ta buga a matsayin manajan Gerard, wanda ya sa ta rage maki takwas a baya da kungiyar ta Hearts.
Minga ta zura kwallo minti bakwai kafin a tashi daga wasan amma Rangers din da ba su da karfin gwiwa sun kasa ramawa.
A yanzu haka Rangers sun koma matsayi na shida, Livingston ta hau zuwa uku, ta hanyar cin nasara a kan Hibernian.
Wani abu da ya bayyana kamar an jefa shi ne ya buge shi a kai kuma ya sa mai kula da jirgin ruwa ya kula da Spencer.
Gerard ya yi canje-canje takwas a tawagar da ta kai wasan karshe na gasar cin kofin Betfred ta shekara ta 2007.
Holt, a akasin wannan, ya saukar da wannan Levi 11 wanda ya sami maki daga Hearts a makon da ya gabata, wanda ya kamata ya yi farin ciki da cewa ƙungiyar da aka horar da su sosai ta mamaye abokan hamayyarsa a kowane mataki.
Duk da cewa Rangers sun mamaye matsayin, Livingston ya yi aiki da kyau da kwallon da suka samu.
A minti na biyu na wasan Menga ta fara wucewa ta farko lokacin da Scott Pittman ya aika zuwa ga Alan McGregor, amma dan wasan tsakiya ya rasa babbar damarsa.
Ko da yake wani ƙwararren ƙwararren Kagan Jacobs ya kai wa Captain Craig Halkett, abokin hamayyarsa Alan Lithgow ya sami damar yin amfani da shi a cikin bayan gida.
Ko da yake Rangers sun ci gaba da zama a kan gaba, amma sun nuna bege fiye da amincewa a wasan da suka buga.
Alfredo Morelos ya yi tunanin cewa ya kamata ya ci kwallo a minti 15 lokacin da ya yi karo da Steven Lawless, amma alƙali Steven Thompson ya ƙi amincewa da ƙarar ɗan Colombia.
A farkon rabin, an samu harbi biyu na Rangers, amma ciwon kai daga Lasana Colibri da kuma bugun da Ovie Izaria ya yi bai dame tsohon mai tsaron ragar Ibrox Liam Kelly ba.
Ko da yake Livy ya ci kwallo a minti na 34, amma idan aka yi amfani da yarjejeniyar su, babu wanda zai iya musun cewa sun cancanci hakan.
Rangers sun sake kasawa wajen sarrafa wani kwarewar da Jacobs ya yi.
Scott Arfield bai amsa ba lokacin da Declan Gallagher ya ba Scott Robinson kwallon. Robinson bai rasa kwanciyar hankali ba, amma ya zaɓi Mangan don kammala mai sauƙi.
Gerard ya amsa ta hanyar saukar da Ryan Kent a madadin Collibaly a lokacin hutu. Wannan canjin ya yi tasiri sosai. Winger ya ci gaba da tafiya tare da Morlowe, amma Kelly mai ban tsoro ya gudu daga layinsa don hana shi.
