Mene ne bikin 'yan kasa na duniya, kuma shin ya yi wani abu don rage talauci?
A ranar Asabar ne za a karbi bakuncin bikin Global Citizen a birnin New York, kuma bikin na shekara-shekara zai kunshi manyan fitattun wakoki da kuma wani muhimmin aiki: kawar da talauci a duniya.
Yanzu a shekara ta bakwai, dubun dubatar mutane suna zuwa babban filin wasa a Central Park don halartar bikin Baƙi na Duniya don jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon Janet Jackson, Cardi B, da Shawn Mendes, da kuma wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin shirin na kawar da matsanancin talauci nan da shekarar 2030.
An fara bikin ne a shekarar 2012 kuma babban cibiyar sadaukar da kai ce ta kasa da kasa, wato Global Citizen Festival.
Don samun tikiti kyauta don halartar wannan taron (sai dai idan ba ku yarda ku biya kuɗin tikitin VIP ba), magoya bayan kide-kide suna buƙatar yin ayyuka da yawa ko "ayyuka"; waɗannan ayyukan sun haɗa da aikin sa kai, imel ko kiran waya ga shugaban duniya, ko wasu hanyoyi masu ma'ana don taimakawa wayar da kan jama'a game da burin su na kawo ƙarshen talauci.
Amma da yake muna da shekara 12 kawai kafin mu cimma wannan burin, yaya nasarar da 'yan ƙasa na duniya suka samu?
Shin bayar da kyautar tikitin kide kide kyauta ga mutane hanya ce ta musamman ta sa mutane su amsa kiran da ake yi musu ko kuma wata hanyar da ake kira "clictivism" - yanayin da mutane ke tunanin suna kawo canji na gaske ta hanyar sanya hannu kan korafi ta yanar gizo ko aika tweet - wani nau'i ne na aikin banza?
Tun daga 2011, Global Citizen ya ce sun rubuta fiye da "aiki" miliyan 19 daga masu tallafawa don taimakawa dandamali na dalilai daban-daban.
Ya ce, wadannan matakan sun taimaka wajen motsa shugabannin duniya su ayyana kudaden da suka kai dala biliyan 37 da suka dace da tabbatar da manufofi da nufin sauya rayuwar mutane sama da biliyan 2.25 nan da shekarar 2030.
A farkon 2018, an zaɓi ƙungiyoyi 390 da kuma sanarwar da suka samo asali daga ayyukansu, sun ba da ko sun tara kuɗi kusan dala biliyan 10.
Kungiyar ta kiyasta cewa kudaden da suka tara sun yi tasiri kai tsaye kan mutane miliyan 649 a duniya.
Daya daga cikin muhimman tabbacin da aka samu, bayan karbar tweets sama da 4,700 daga 'yan kasa na duniya, shine cewa an basu kyautar dala miliyan 35 don taimakawa kasar ta kawo karshen matsalar rashin abinci mai gina jiki a Rwanda.
Tare da goyon bayan gwamnatin Burtaniya, masu ba da gudummawa, gwamnatocin ƙasa da 'yan ƙasa na duniya kamar ku, za mu iya kawo ƙarshen rashin adalci na zamantakewar rashin abinci mai gina jiki a tarihi, "in ji Tracy Ullman, jakadan samar da abinci mai gina jiki, ga taron a wani taron raye-raye a London a watan Afrilu 2018.
Bayan daukar matakai sama da 5,000 da suka bukaci Burtaniya da ta inganta abinci mai gina jiki ga uwaye da yara, Gwamnati ta sanar da bayar da tallafi ga shirin nan mai suna Power of Nutrition, wanda zai kai ga mata da yara miliyan 5 a matsayin abinci mai gina jiki.
Tambaya ɗaya da ake yawan yi a dandalinsa ita ce, "Me ya sa kake ganin za a iya kawar da matsanancin talauci?"
Global Citizen ya amsa: "Zai zama hanya mai tsawo da wahala - wani lokacin za mu faɗi kuma mu gaza.
Amma kamar babban motsi na kare hakkin bil'adama da kuma na nuna bambanci, za mu yi nasara domin idan muka hada kai za mu fi karfi.
A wannan shekara, taron da aka yi a New York zai nuna Janet Jackson, Weekend, Shawn Mendes, Cardi B, Janelle Moni, kuma Deborah-Lee Furness da Huff Jackman ne za su ba da bakuncin.
Sakataren Harkokin Cikin Gida: Amurka na iya amfani da Sojojin Ruwa a matsayin "ƙuntatawa" don hana fitar da makamashin Rasha
Sakataren harkokin cikin gida na Amurka Ryan Zincke ya bayyana cewa Washington na iya neman taimakon sojan ruwa don hana makamashi na Rasha isa kasuwanni "idan ya cancanta", in ji Washington Examiner.
Zincke ya yi zargin cewa, Rasha ta shiga Syria ne don neman sabbin kasuwanni, amma ya kamata a lura cewa Rasha tana shiga Syria ne saboda gayyatar da aka yi mata daga gwamnatin Syria.
Ya ce, "Ina ganin suna shiga tsakani ne a Gabas ta Tsakiya domin suna son zama masu samar da makamashi a Gabas ta Tsakiya kamar yadda suke yi a Gabashin Turai da kudancin Turai".
A cewar wannan jami'in, akwai hanyoyi da hanyoyin da za a magance wannan.
Ya ce, Amurka tana da karfin da za ta tabbatar da cewa hanyoyin ruwa sun kasance a bude, kuma idan ya cancanta, ta hana makamashin su shiga kasuwa, saboda tana da rundunar sojan ruwa, in ji shi.
Sinke yana jawabi ne a taron da kungiyar Consumer Energy Alliance ta shirya, kungiyar da ke ba da agaji da ke kiran kanta "muryar masu amfani da makamashi" a Amurka.
Ya kwatanta tsarin Washington da na Rasha da Iran, ya kuma nuna cewa a aikace su daya ne.
