Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce za ta yanke "ƙuduri mai ƙarfi" game da neman shugabancin Amurka a 2020
Sanata Elizabeth Warren ta Massachusetts ta ce a ranar Asabar za ta yanke "ƙuduri mai ƙarfi" game da neman shugabancin ƙasar bayan zaɓen tsakiyar shekara.
Ta tabbatar wa Warren cewa zai yi la'akari da yin gasa a wani taron gari a Holyoke, Massachusetts.
"Lokaci ya yi da mata za su je Washington su gyara gwamnatinmu da ta lalace, kuma lokaci ya yi da za a bukaci mace a kan mulki", in ji ta, in ji The Hill.
"Bayan 6 ga watan Nuwamba, zan dauki takarar shugaban kasa da muhimmanci".
