Ta ce, "Ina matukar damuwa da abin da Donald Trump ke yi wa dimokiradiyarmu.
Warren ya kasance mai sukar Trump da kuma wanda aka zaba a Kotun Koli Brett Kavanaugh.
"Muna bukatar binciken FBI kafin mu rubuta kuri'ar", in ji Warren a shafinsa na Twitter a ranar Juma'a.
