Jakadan Amurka ya zargi China da amfani da 'tallace-tallacen farfaganda' wajen yin barazana
Mako guda bayan da wata jaridar kasar Sin ta wallafa wani shafi hudu na talla a wata jaridar Amurka game da amfanin cinikin Amurka da China, jakadan Amurka a China ya zargi Beijing da amfani da kafofin yada labaran Amurka don yada farfagandar kasar Sin.
Shugaban na Amurka ya ambaci karin da China Daily ta bayar a jaridar Des Moines Register - jaridar da ta fi sayarwa a jihar Iowa - bayan zargin cewa China na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben majalisar dattijai na ranar 6 ga watan Nuwamba.
Jami'an Amurka sun shaida wa Reuters cewa zargin da Trump ya yi na cewa Beijing na kokarin tsoma baki a zaben Amurka wani sabon mataki ne na kara tsananta yakin neman zaben da Washington ke yi don matsawa kasar Sin.
Duk da cewa ya zama ruwan dare gama gari ga gwamnatocin kasashen waje su yi tallace-tallace don bunkasa kasuwanci, dangantakar da ke tsakanin Beijing da Washington ta shiga cikin yakin cinikayya mai tsanani, inda kasashen biyu suka kara yawan harajin shigo da kayayyaki da juna.
A yakin cinikayya, kasar Sin ta kara yawan harajin shigo da kayayyaki a baya, ta mayar da martani ga Amurka, kuma masana tattalin arziki a China da Amurka sun ce an tsara sabon harajin ne don yin hari kan kamfanonin shigo da kayayyaki a jihohi kamar Iowa, wadanda ke goyon bayan jam'iyyar Republican ta Trump.
Terry Branstad, jakadan Amurka a China kuma mai dadewa a matsayin gwamnan Iowa, kuma mai mallakar daya daga cikin manyan kamfanonin da ke fitar da kayayyakin gona zuwa kasar Sin, ya ce Beijing ta bata wa ma'aikata, manoma da kuma kasuwancin Amurka rai.
"China yanzu tana kara yawan barazanar ta hanyar yada farfaganda a cikin kafafen yada labarai masu zaman kansu", in ji Bransted a cikin shafin rubutu na Des Moines Register a ranar Lahadi.
A cikin wani rahoto da aka wallafa a jaridar Des Moines Register, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta yi amfani da 'yancin fadin albarkacin baki da' yancin yada labarai da Amurka ke karfafawa don yada farfaganda.
"A akasin wannan, a kan labaran labarai a titunan Beijing, za ku ga iyakancewar muryoyin rashin jituwa, kuma ba za ku ga ainihin ra'ayoyin da jama'ar kasar Sin za su iya yi game da matsalar tattalin arzikin kasar Sin ba, saboda kafofin watsa labarai suna karkashin yatsan jam'iyyar kwaminis ta kasar Sin", in ji shi.
Ya kuma rubuta cewa "wani daga cikin manyan jaridun kasar Sin ya yi watsi da alkawarin buga labarinsa", amma bai ambaci jaridar da ya wallafa ba.
Masu bincike sun ce, a yayin da ake ci gaba da samun tashin hankali a Kavanaugh, mata masu jefa kuri'a a jam'iyyar Republican za su yi yawa kafin zaben.
Wani masanin siyasa ya yi gargadin cewa jam'iyyar Republican za ta fuskanci kalubale a lokacin zaben da ke tafe, musamman daga mata, saboda manyan shugabannin jam'iyyar Republican da dama sun goyi bayan dan takarar kotun koli Brett Kavanaugh, wanda ke fuskantar zargin cin zarafin mata.
Jin daɗi game da wannan yana da girma sosai, kuma yawancin 'yan Republican sun riga sun ga cewa suna son ci gaba da jefa kuri'a.
Babu wata hanyar komawa baya ga waɗannan abubuwan", in ji Grant Rehr, farfesa a fannin kimiyyar siyasa a Makarantar Maxwell a Jami'ar Syracuse, a wata kasida da aka buga a The Hill a ranar Asabar.
Rehr ya ce yana tsammanin bukatar da Sanata Jeff Flake (R-Arizona) ya yi a lokacin da ya bukaci FBI ta gudanar da bincike ba zai isa ya kwantar da masu jefa kuri'a ba.
"Mata ba za su manta da abin da ya faru jiya ba - ba za su manta da shi ba a gobe ko a watan Nuwamba", in ji Karin Jean Pierre, babban mai ba da shawara da kuma kakakin mata na kasar na kungiyar cigaba ta Moon, a ranar Juma'a, Washington DC ta ruwaito.
Mike ya ruwaito cewa a safiyar ranar Juma'a, masu zanga-zangar sun yi zanga-zanga a cikin majalisa, suna ihu "Nuwamba tana zuwa!" saboda Dr. Christine Blasey Ford ta rantsar da ita, kuma kwamitin shari'a na Republican ya yanke shawarar ci gaba da takarar Kavanaugh.
"Jami'ar Democrat tana gab da rasa himma da kuma kwarin gwiwarta", in ji Stu Rothenberg, wanda ke nazarin siyasa ba tare da son zuciya ba, ya shaida wa shafin labarai.
"Mutane suna cewa ya riga ya yi girma; gaskiya ne.
Amma akwai sauran hanyoyi da za su kara yawaita, musamman tsakanin mata masu jefa kuri'a a yankunan karkara da kuma matasa masu shekaru 18 zuwa 29 wadanda ba sa son shugaban kasa amma kuma ba sa yawan kada kuri'a".
Tun kafin a fara gabatar da shaidar da Ford ya yi game da zargin cin zarafin mata a gaban kotun koli, manazarta sun yi hasashen cewa idan Republican ya ci gaba da tabbatar da hakan, za a fuskanci kalubale.
"Wannan yana da matsala ga GOP", in ji tsohon shugaban kwamitin Republican na kasa Michael Steele a makon da ya gabata, in ji NBC News.
"Wannan ba kawai game da kuri'ar kwamitin ba ne ko kuma game da kuri'ar karshe ko za a nada Kavanaugh a kan benci, amma game da yadda 'yan Republican suka bi da zargin da kuma yadda 'yan Republican suka bi da wadanda aka kashe", in ji Guy Szil, darektan kungiyar da ke taimakawa 'yan Democrat su zabi, kamar yadda kafar yada labarai ta ruwaito.
Koyaya, Amurkawa suna da ra'ayi daban-daban game da wanda zasu amince dashi a cikin yanayin asalin rantsuwar Ford da Cavanaugh, suna ba da fifiko ga amincewa da Cavanaugh.
Wani sabon binciken da Yugav ya yi ya nuna cewa kashi 41 cikin dari na mutane sun gaskata da rantsuwar da Ford ya yi, kuma kashi 35 cikin dari sun ce sun gaskata da Kavanaugh.
