Mutanen garin sun tuna da firist na Ikilisiyar Ingila wanda ya lashe Victoria Cross a matsayin mai yaki a yakin duniya na farko.
Lt. Col. Reverend Bernard Van ya lashe lambar yabo a ranar 29 ga watan Satumba, 1918, saboda ya shiga cikin hare-haren da aka yi a Bellenglyce da Lehigh Court.
Duk da haka, bayan kwana hudu, wani mai harbi ya kashe shi, kuma bai taba sanin cewa an ba shi lambar yabo mafi girma ta Birtaniya ba.
