Tom Daley ya ce ya ji "rashin jin daɗi" game da jima'i
Masanin wasan motsa jiki na Olympics Tom Daly ya ce ya girma yana jin cewa ya kasa wasu saboda jinsi - amma wannan ya sa Daly ya yi nasara.
"Ba kowa ba ne kamar ni", in ji ɗan shekara ashirin da huɗu, "sai da na shiga makarantar sakandare".
Da yake magana a kan Radio 4 Desert Island Discs na farko wanda Lauren LaVerne ya gabatar, ya yi magana game da 'yancin gay da ke ba wasu "bege".
Ya ce zama iyaye ya rage sha'awarsa na samun gasar Olympics.
Kirsty Young, mai gabatar da wasan kwaikwayon na dogon lokaci, ya yi watanni da yawa saboda rashin lafiya.
Dali ya zauna a cikin jirgin ruwa a farkon shirin LaVonne, yana cewa yana jin "ƙananan" fiye da sauran yayin da yake girma saboda "al'umma ba ta yarda da sha'awar yara maza da mata daidai ba".
Ya ce: "Jin cewa na fi wasu da kuma bambancin da nake da shi ne ainihin abin da ya ba ni ƙarfin yin nasara".
Ya ce yana so ya tabbatar da cewa shi "wani abu ne" don haka bai yi takaici ba lokacin da kowa ya san game da jima'i.
Dali, wanda ya lashe lambar tagulla sau biyu a gasar Olympics, yanzu ya zama babban mai yada labaran LGBT, kuma ya yi amfani da kasancewarsa a wasannin Commonwealth da aka yi a Ostiraliya a wannan shekara don yin kira ga wasu ƙasashe su halatta transgender.
Ya ce ya bayyana hakan ne saboda yana jin cewa yana da sa'ar rayuwa a fili ba tare da wata illa ba kuma yana son ya ba wasu "bege".
Dali, wanda ya lashe gasar cin kofin duniya sau uku, ya ce "ya ba ni mamaki" da ya ƙaunaci wani mutum, mai shirya fina-finai na Amurka Dustin Lance Black, wanda ya sadu da shi a shekarar 2013.
Ya ce Dalí ta auri wani mai lashe Oscar wanda ya girme ta da shekara 20, amma bambancin shekaru bai taba zama matsala ba.
"Lokacin da kake fuskantar matsaloli da yawa a irin wannan ƙuruciya" - Dali ya fara shiga gasar Olympics lokacin da yake ɗan shekara 14, kuma mahaifinsa ya mutu daga ciwon daji shekaru uku bayan haka - ya ce yana da wuya a sadu da wani ɗan shekara ɗaya wanda ya fuskanci irin hawa da sauka da kansa.
A watan Yuni, ma'aurata sun zama iyayen ɗan Robert Ray Black-Dale, wanda Dali ya ce ya canza "dukkanin ra'ayinsa".
"Idan ka tambaye ni a bara, zan yi magana game da 'Ina son lashe lambar zinare,'" in ji shi.
"Ka sani, akwai abubuwa da yawa da suka fi zinare na Olympics muhimmanci.
Robbie ne zinariyar zinare ta Olympics".
Bayan an gano ciwon daji a kwakwalwa, a shekara ta 2011, a shekara ta 40, Dali ya ba da sunan mahaifinsa Robert.
Mahaifinsa bai taba yarda cewa zai mutu ba, kuma ya tambayi shi a ƙarshe idan har yanzu yana da tikiti don London 2012 saboda Dalí ya ce yana so ya gan shi a gaban fage.
"Amma ban iya cewa 'Babu uba ba har sai na zauna a gaban layi na gani,'" in ji shi.
"Na riƙe hannunsa har sai da ya yi numfashi na ƙarshe, kuma lokacin da numfashin ya tsaya kuma ya mutu ne kawai na yarda cewa ba shi da ƙarfi", in ji shi.
A shekara mai zuwa, Daly ya yi gasa a gasar Olympics ta 2012 kuma ya lashe tagulla.
Ya ce, "Na san wannan shine burina na tsawon rayuwata, ba abin da ya fi wannan jin dadi fiye da yin sallama a gaban jama'ar kasarmu a gasar Olympics.
Wannan ya kuma ba shi wahayi don zaɓar waƙar farko - Heather Sman's Pride - waƙar da ta yi masa magana har zuwa gasar Olympics, har yanzu yana jin daɗin jin wannan waƙar.
