Ryder Cup ranar Asabar ba ta sa Mickelson ya sauka ba.
A ranar Lahadi, Phil Mickelson na Amurka zai buga wasan Ryder Cup karo na 47 kuma zai kafa tarihi, amma zai bukaci ya gyara yadda yake wasa don kada ya zama wani muhimmin ci gaba.
A ranar Asabar ne kyaftin Jim Furik ya fitar da Mickelson a raga biyu da hudu, wanda ya zama karo na 12 a gasar da ake yi a shekara biyu.
Maimakon ya yi wasa a kan raga kamar yadda yake yi a Amurka, ya yi amfani da ransa a kan raga don ya ƙarfafa wasu kuma ya magance matsalolin da ya fuskanta.
Duk da cewa ya kasance a saman sahunsa, dan wasan mai shekara 48 da ya kasa yin daidai da kwallon bai dace da filin golf na Lae National ba, inda ake samun ciyawa mai yawa da ke azabtar da kuskuren harbi.
Ko da yake wannan filin wasan ba shi da wahala, Mickelson a ranar Lahadi zai fuskanci a wasa na tara da Francesco Molinari, zakaran Birtaniya na farko a kan lokaci. Ya yi tarayya da sabon shiga Tommy Fleetwood don lashe dukkan wasanninsu hudu a wannan makon.
Idan Amurkawa da ke da maki hudu a kasa suka fara wasa a wasanni 12 na raga, to wasan Mickelson zai zama mai muhimmanci.
Furik ya nuna amincewarsa ga dan wasansa, ba wai zai ce ba.
"Ya fahimci cikakken rawar da zai taka a yau, ya yi min magana kuma ya ce zai kasance a shirye gobe", in ji Furik.
Yana da tabbaci sosai a kansa.
Ya yi aiki sosai a wannan makon da kuma a baya.
Wataƙila ban taɓa tunanin cewa zai buga wasanni biyu ba.
Na yi tunani sosai, amma wannan shine yadda ya faru.
Yana son ya shiga filin wasa kamar sauran.
A ranar Lahadi, Mickelson zai doke Nick Faldo, wanda ya fi kowacce wasa a gasar Ryder Cup.
Wannan zai zama ƙarshen aikin Ryder Cup ga wani ɗan wasa wanda bai kai matsayin da ya dace ba.
Furik ya ce Mickelson ya yi nasara 18 da 20 da kuma raga bakwai. Duk da haka, kasancewarsa ya kawo abubuwa da yawa da ba za a iya rasawa ba.
"Yana da ban dariya, yana da ban dariya, yana da ban dariya, yana son yin dariya da mutane, kuma babban mutum ne da ya kamata ya kasance a cikin tawagar", in ji Furik.
Ina ganin matasa 'yan wasa sun ji daɗin fuskantar shi a wannan makon.
Zai ba da fiye da wasa kawai.
Kyaftin din Turai Thomas John ya san cewa babban jagoran zai ɓace nan da nan.
Shugaban kungiyar Turai, Thomas John ya san cewa idan aka kai ga ranar karshe ta gasar Ryder Cup, za a iya cin nasara.
Dane ya fara wasa a Valderrama a 1997, inda tawagar da aka jagoranci da Seve Ballesteros ta ci gaba da samun maki biyar a kan Amurkawa, amma sun zo kan iyakar iyakar, suna cin nasara da 141⁄2-131⁄2 .
"Kuna tunatar da kanku cewa muna da babban gubar a Valderrama; muna da babban gubar a Brookline, mun rasa a can, mun ci a Valderrama, don haka nasara ce kawai", in ji John, yana mai tsokaci ne a kan zaman da ya yi a ranar Lahadi inda tawagar John ta ci gaba da 5-3 da kuma 10-6 a jiya a Le Golf International.
Saboda haka tarihi ya nuna min da sauran 'yan'uwa a tawagarmu cewa wannan ba ƙarshen ba ne.
Za ka iya zama mai ban sha'awa a gobe.
Ka yi sauri ka daina wannan halin kuma ka yi abin da ya dace.
Babu abin da ya ƙare har sai kun sami maki a kan allon.
Muna da manufa guda, kuma ita ce mu ci wannan kofin, kuma wannan shine abin da muke mai da hankali a kai.
A koyaushe ina cewa ina mai da hankali ne kan 'yan wasa 12 a tawagar, amma a gefe guda kuma mun san su sosai - su ne mafi kyawun 'yan wasa a duniya".
John ya yi farin ciki da yadda tawagarsa ta yi a kan wani filin golf mai tsauri, ya kara da cewa: "Ba zan taɓa yin nasara a kan kaina ba.
Amma gobe dabba ce dabam.
A yau, mutane suna yin zanga-zanga, amma gobe wani abu ne dabam.
Yana da kyau a kasance a kan hanya tare da abokin tarayya lokacin da abubuwa ke da kyau, amma idan kun kasance a kan hanya kadai, za a gwada ku sosai a matsayin mai wasan golf.
Wannan shine sakon da ya kamata ku ba wa 'yan wasan ku, ku kawo mafi kyawunku gobe.
Yanzu, kana barin abokin tarayya, kuma dole ne ya fita ya kawo mafi kyawunsa".
Ba kamar John ba, Jim Furyk abokin hamayyarsa yana da ra'ayi na gaba, yana buƙatar 'yan wasan suyi aiki da kansu maimakon abokan tarayya, banda Jordan Speith da Justin Thomas, waɗanda suka sami maki uku cikin huɗu.
Fury ya ga bangarorin biyu na wannan babban wasan da ke gudana a ranar ƙarshe ta mala'iku, Fury na daga cikin tawagar da ta lashe a Brooklyn, kuma ta rasa lokacin da Turai ta fitar da "Miracle of Medina".
A ranar karshe, a lokacin da aka tambaye shi yadda Ben Crenshaw, wanda ya jagoranci kungiyar a shekarar 1999, ya tsara 'yan wasansa, ya ce, "Na tuna da kowane abu".
"Muna da manyan wasanni 12 gobe, amma kuna son samun saurin farawa kamar yadda kuka gani a Brookline, kamar yadda kuka gani a Madina.
Idan saurin ya tafi a wata hanya, matsin lamba na iya zama mai yawa a tsakiyar wasanni.
Mun tsara jerin 'yan wasanmu, mun tsara yadda za mu yi wasa, kuma muna so mu yi sihiri gobe".
An ba Thomas aikin jagorancin sake dawowa, kuma a cikin wasan farko zai fuskanci Rory McIlroy, yayin da Paul Casey, Justin Ross, John Raham, Tommy Fleetwood, da Ian Puller su ne sauran Turawa da suka zo a farkon rabin.
"Na tafi tare da wannan rukuni a wannan tsari, saboda ina tsammanin yana da kyau a kowane fanni", in ji John game da zaɓin da ya yi na 'yan mata.
An sake jinkirta aikin sabon jirgin yakin Jamus.
An shirya sabon jirgin yakin na rundunar sojan ruwa ta Jamus da za a fara aiki a shekarar 2014 don maye gurbin tsofaffin jiragen yakin da aka yi amfani da su a lokacin Cold War, amma kafofin yada labarai na gida sun ruwaito cewa ba za a fara aiki ba har sai a kalla shekara mai zuwa saboda tsarin da ba daidai ba da kuma farashin dusar ƙanƙara.
Jaridar Die Zeit ta ruwaito, tana ambaton wani kakakin soji, cewa an dage aikin "Rheinland-Falls", wanda shine babban jirgi na sabon rukunin jiragen ruwa na Baden-Württemberg, zuwa farkon rabin shekarar 2019.
An yi niyyar samun jirgin a cikin 2014, amma matsalolin da aka fuskanta kafin isar da shi sun shafi makomar shirin Pride.
A shekarar 2007, rundunar sojan ruwa ta umarci jiragen ruwa hudu na Baden-Württemberg don maye gurbin tsoffin jiragen ruwa na Bremen.
An san cewa jiragen ruwa za su kasance da manyan bindigogi da makamai masu linzami da makamai masu linzami da jiragen ruwa da kuma wasu fasahohin sirri kamar su radar, infrared da siginar sauti.
Wani muhimmin fasali kuma shine ba a buƙatar yin gyare-gyare na dogon lokaci, don haka ya kamata a iya tura sabbin jiragen ruwa daga tashar jiragen ruwa na gida, har zuwa shekaru biyu.
Duk da haka, Die Seat ya nuna cewa jinkirin jinkirin jinkirta aiki yana nufin cewa waɗannan jiragen ruwa masu fasaha masu tasowa za su zama tsofaffi a lokacin da suka shiga sabis; ana cewa waɗannan jiragen ruwa sun ba da damar Jamus ta nuna ikonta a ƙasashen waje.
An yi ta samun labarin fashin da aka yi wa jiragen yakin F125 a bara, lokacin da rundunar sojin ruwa ta Jamus ta hana su aiki kuma ta mayar da su zuwa sansanin jiragen ruwa na Hamburg Blohm & Voss.
Wannan shi ne karo na farko a tarihin sojan ruwa da aka mayar da shi ga mai gina jirgin bayan an karɓi jigilar kaya.
Babu wanda ya san dalilin da ya sa aka mayar da jirgin, amma kafofin watsa labarai na Jamus sun ba da rahoton cewa jirgin yana da "abubuwan da suka shafi software da kayan aiki" da yawa kuma saboda haka ba za a iya amfani da jirgin ba idan aka tura shi aikin yaƙi.
Rashin software yana da mahimmanci saboda ƙungiyar mutane 120 da ke da rabin rabin ma'aikatan jirgin ruwan tsohuwar jirgin ruwan Bremen za su sarrafa sabon jirgin ruwan Baden-Württemberg.
Bugu da kari, an samu rahotanni cewa jirgin yana da nauyi sosai, wanda zai rage aikin jirgin kuma zai iyakance ikon sojojin na gaba don yin sabbin abubuwa.
An yi imanin cewa "Rhineland-Falz" mai nauyin tan 7,000 ya ninka nauyin jirgi na wannan nau'in da aka yi amfani da shi a yakin duniya na biyu.
Ko da yake barin kayan aiki mara kyau, farashin dukan aikin - ciki har da horar da ma'aikatan - ya zama matsala.
Ko da yake an fara sa ran kudin zai kai €2.2 biliyan, yanzu an ce ya kai €3.1 ($3.6 biliyan).
A cikin hasken kwanan nan game da faɗakarwar cewa ƙarfin jirgin ruwan Jamus yana raguwa, matsalolin da ke shafar sabbin jiragen ruwa na yaƙi sun zama masu mahimmanci.
A farkon wannan shekarar, Hans-Peter Bartels, shugaban kwamitin tsaro na majalisar dokokin Jamus, ya yarda cewa a zahiri "jiragen ruwa masu iya aiki suna ɓacewa" a cikin jirgin ruwa.
Jami'ai sun ce matsalolin suna kara rikitarwa yayin da tsofaffin jiragen ruwa ke kwance amma ba a samun sabbin jiragen ruwa a kowane lokaci.
