"Suna son su yi suna da sunana.
Wannan abu ne na halitta.
Suna son su yi suna da sunana, amma hakan wani ɓangare ne na aikin.
"Na yi farin ciki, ina lafiya", in ji ta da murmushi.
A dangane da zargin, lauyoyin Ronaldo na shirin shigar da kara kan Der Spiegel, wanda Reuters ta ce lauyoyin sun bayyana shi a matsayin wani rahoto mara izini game da shakku a fagen sirri.
Lauyan dan wasan, Christian Scherzinger, ya bayyana cewa dan wasan zai nemi diyya don "lalacewar dabi'a mai tsanani kamar keta doka", ya kara da cewa, "Wannan shine daya daga cikin manyan keta hakkin mutum a cikin 'yan kwanakin nan".
An ce an yi wannan zargin ne a watan Yuni na shekarar 2009 a wani daki a Otel din Palms da gidan caca a Las Vegas.
