Labaran Red Tide: Yanayin ya ragu a yankunan Pinellas, Manatee da Sarasota
A cewar rahoton da Hukumar Kifi da Daji ta Florida ta fitar, an samu raguwar yawan 'yan tsiraru a yankin Tampa.
A cewar FWC, an bayar da rahoton yanayin fashewar fashewar a lardunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier, wanda ke nuna alamar raguwar tsanani.
A cikin yankunan bakin teku daga arewacin Penelope zuwa kudu maso kudu, ana ganin red tides (ƙaddamar da raƙuman ruwa) suna tasowa a cikin kimanin mil 130 a cikin wani ruwa.
An ga wasu wurare a cikin lardin Hillsborough da ke da nisan mil 10 daga bakin teku, amma ba su da yawa kamar yadda aka gani a baya.
An kuma samu wani mummunan yanayi a yankin Pasco.
A makon da ya gabata, an samu alamun ruwa mai zafi a yankunan bakin teku na lardin Pinellas, da ƙananan da manyan a yankunan bakin teku na Hillsborough, da ƙananan ƙananan ko manyan a lardin Manatee, da ƙananan ƙananan ko manyan a lardin Sarasota, da ƙananan ƙananan ko manyan a lardin Charlotte, da ƙananan ƙananan ko manyan a lardin Leviathan, da kuma ƙananan yankunan da ke nesa da yankin Korea.
Matsalar numfashi ta ci gaba a lardunan Pinellas, Manatee, Sarasota, Lee da Collier.
Amma babu rahoton ciwon numfashi a arewa maso yammacin Florida a cikin makonni da suka gabata.
